            <!-- MODULE 2 -->
            <article class="module--box-shadow-gradient-bg-green-moderate u-span-2" id="technical-skills">
                <span class="module__eyebrow">Technical Skills</span>
                <header class="module__title">
                    <h2 class="module__heading">
                        How This Site Is Built
                    </h2>
                    <p class="module__subheading">
                        A modern, performance-first web stack designed for scalability, SEO, and maintainability. </p>
                </header>
                <section class="card">
                    <header>
                        <h3 class="card__heading">
                            Architecture
                        </h3>
                        <p class="card__subheading">
                            Built for stability, speed, and scale
                        </p>
                    </header>
                    <p class="card__body">
                        This site is structured as a
                        <span class="font-weight-700 text-color--emphasis">
                            modular, server-rendered system
                        </span>
                        to provide fast initial load times, predictable performance,
                        and full crawlability by search engines. This architecture favors deterministic builds and stable
                        deployments,
                        prioritizing real-world performance metrics while avoiding unnecessary client-side complexity.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="card">
                    <header>
                        <h3 class="card__heading">
                            Rendering
                        </h3>
                        <p class="card__subheading">
                            Server-Side Rendering for Speed and SEO
                        </p>
                    </header>
                    <p class="card__body">
                        Pages are rendered as complete HTML on the server,
                        delivering faster first paint, consistent content for search
                        engines, and
                        <span class="font-weight-700 text-color--emphasis">
                            stable Core Web Vitals</span>—without relying on heavy client-side processing or delayed page assembly.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="card">
                    <header>
                        <h3 class="card__heading">
                            Styling & Maintainability
                        </h3>
                        <p class="card__subheading">
                            Scalable CSS with Enterprise Design Systems in Mind
                        </p>
                    </header>
                    <p class="card__body">
                        Styles are built using semantic, BEM-structured CSS with global design variables. This guarantees
                        <span class="font-weight-700 text-color--emphasis">
                            responsive behavior across devices
                        </span>
                        and makes the system easy to scale, update, and maintain.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="card">
                    <header>
                        <h3 class="card__heading">
                            SEO & Accessibility
                        </h3>
                        <p class="card__subheading">
                            Built for Discoverability and Usability
                        </p>
                    </header>
                    <p class="card__body">
                        Semantic HTML, structured heading hierarchy, accessible navigation patterns, and
                        performance-friendly assets ensure the site is
                        <span class="font-weight-700 text-color--emphasis">
                            optimized for both search engines and real
                            users</span>—without sacrificing design quality.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </article>
            <!-- MODULE 3 -->
            <article class="module--box-shadow-bg-grey u-span-2" id="impact-highlights">
