                        Common challenges across complex, high-traffic web environments—and how they’re addressed.
                    </p>
                </header>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Conversion plateaus despite strong traffic
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Mapped funnel drop-offs, designed targeted experiments, and unlocked measurable conversion lifts and engagement without
                        increasing acquisition spend.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Global sites that don’t scale cleanly
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Reduced global launch friction by centralizing templates and workflows across languages, regions, and regulatory
                        constraints.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Unstructured or low-impact experimentation
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                            Built experimentation discipline by tying every test to a decision, insight, or next action while prioritizing backlogs.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Slow or fragmented web workflows
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Removed bottlenecks and increased velocity by standardizing tooling, ownership, and handoffs across marketing, design,
                        and engineering.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Strategy disconnected from execution
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Ensured every web initiative shipped with defined success metrics and a clear measurement plan.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Cross-functional friction slowing delivery
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Clear ownership, delivery tracking through shared project management tools, and sustained buy-in from all primary
                        stakeholders.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </article>
