                                <span>AI as an accelerator, not a
                                    replacement.</span>
                                I use AI to move faster and think more clearly—while strategy, judgment, and execution
                                remain fully
                                human.
                            </p>
                        </section>
                        <section class="swiper-slide ai-carousel__slide">
                            <p class="ai-carousel__text">
                                <span>Applied where it adds leverage.</span>
                                Across this site, AI supported early ideation, technical validation, and UX and SEO
                                decision-making.
                            </p>
                        </section>
                        <section class="swiper-slide ai-carousel__slide">
                            <p class="ai-carousel__text">
                                <span class="">Reviewed and approved manually.</span>
                                Final code structure, semantic markup, and performance tradeoffs were reviewed, refined,
                                and
                                approved manually.
                            </p>
                        </section>
                        <section class="swiper-slide ai-carousel__slide">
                            <p class="ai-carousel__text">
                                <span>Faster iteration, stronger
                                    outcomes.</span>
                                AI reduced iteration time, surfaced alternatives, and helped challenge assumptions
                                before committing
                                to solutions.
                            </p>
                        </section>
                        <section class="swiper-slide ai-carousel__slide">
                            <p class="ai-carousel__text">
                                <span>How I apply AI at work.</span>
                                I use AI to accelerate analysis and iteration, freeing time for judgment, prioritization, and high-impact decisions.
                            </p>
                        </section>
                        <section class="swiper-slide ai-carousel__slide">
                            <p class="ai-carousel__text">
                                <span>AI with guardrails.</span>
                                I avoid AI in scenarios involving privacy, compliance, or irreversible product
                                decisions—where human
                                oversight is essential.
                            </p>
                        </section>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-pagination ai-carousel__pagination"></div>
                </div>
