                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            What types of roles or projects are you most interested in?
                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p>
                                I do my best work on website optimization and experimentation, where disciplined execution and data-driven decisions
                                drive acquisition, engagement, and long-term revenue impact.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item">
                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            Are you more technical or strategic?
                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p>
                                Both, by design. I work comfortably in code, analytics, and experimentation tools, while communicating tradeoffs,
                                impact, and outcomes clearly across technical and non-technical teams.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item">
                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            Why not use a CMS or website builder for this site?
                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p>
                                This site is intentionally custom-built to demonstrate how I think about
                                performance,
                                scalability, and maintainability. For many organizations, a CMS is the right
                                choice—but
                                understanding what’s happening under the hood is critical to making good decisions
                                at
                                scale.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item">
                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            What makes you different from other web marketers?
                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p>
                                I concentrate on work that holds up over time—prioritizing improvements that stakeholders can measure, with clean
                                execution and operational foundations that support long-term maintainability.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item">
                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            Is this site still a work in progress?
                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p>
                                Yes—by design. The site follows the same MVP-and-iterate philosophy I use
                                professionally. It will continue to evolve as new ideas, experiments, and learnings
                                emerge.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>
                </section>
            </article>

